== Change Nic Profile for a specific VM ==
Use the Put method to change the VM’s nic profile at http://yourServer:port/ovirt-engine/api/vms/specificVmId/nics/specificNicID

Add a header for using xml: Content-Type: application/xml

Add a body(data) with your desired profile(taken from the list above): 
For example:
<nic><br>
<vnic_profile href="/ovirt-engine/api/vnicprofiles/874a3706-62af-40ca-9c0e-7d1a1e92ae02" id="874a3706-62af-40ca-9c0e-7d1a1e92ae02"> </vnic_profile><br>
</nic><br>


